{"tid":257292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：足總盃決賽不會是我最後一場比賽","createTime":"2017-05-25T07:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T07:21:00.000Z","uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e993605c1ce3123f4d7d8ed95515b049d0ede8f3","tid":257292,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/280/18112062280/18118474385_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F280%2F18112062280%2F18118474385_600x399.jpg&h=46dd8ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=3%2Fyb9fo0OzuLUwrjyftdmtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f26d3881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加被問到周末對車路士的英足盃決賽，可會是最後一次領「兵」出戰時，他沒有正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n「我不知道，無論如何這不會是我最後一場比賽，因為我會留在足球界。」雲加在剛才的記者會上，被問到這個尷尬問題時，沒有正面回應。本季阿仙奴未能以英超前4名成績完成，是該名法國籍名帥首次未能領「兵」出戰歐聯，因而引起外界推測他完成周末之戰後，可能會退位。<br />\n<br />\n本季阿仙奴長期受傷「兵」困擾，這場決賽亦沒例外，其中基比爾包列斯達因傷將會休戰6至8星期，與另一傷將梅斯達菲及今仗停賽的哥斯尼都避戰，可幸雲加指最受注視的阿歷斯山齊士無恙，但須通過賽前測試才可列陣。<br />\n<br />\n「以他（阿歷斯山齊士）的個性，以他對球會的投入，他將會盡一切努力在周末落場。」雲加說。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp18112062280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp18112062280&d=3%2Fyb9fo0OzuLUwrjyftdmtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=37efe506\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp18112062280&h=6c264a1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp18112062280</a>"},{"pid":"15f55243f2ed38cdc47feaf509c853a2ebdbcc0f","tid":257292,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c7f220d07371d329ecbf8ff5fa7dda6f77b67c","tid":257292,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"永繼電加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f697191044ae103bb38b3bd7742f01256c2fac","tid":257292,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永續電加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f2f3919ef20c7900ac93031370f20b55757e1c9","tid":257292,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>永續電叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c25e9885d0f693ebbfc44e27c76344775de3ba2f","tid":257292,"uid":15370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"足總杯應該會放比電叻<br />\n博佢永續"},{"pid":"2ef85ac1fd79e59bbd68e0095fcbd6327a7878c5","tid":257292,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>足總杯應該會放比電叻<br />\n博佢永續</blockquote><br />\n希望足總盃輸埋但係照續約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efa09b8a55afcfad11b274b8ba36badac971f3d","tid":257292,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c3a89ef6a14eecc495da242bee033b5eeb18a9","tid":257292,"uid":1147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"幫電叻含啦你班25"}]}